divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my deck at my apartment and I was looking up at the sky and watching planes and helicopters fly around and make landings at the various airports in the area. I looked up above the tree line and a pulsating white light that was up in the sky. I noticed that everytime that it pulsated it was in a different location in the sky. It was going every which way everytime it would light up again. I continued to watch for about 5 minutes and then it was gone. It was showing up in all different directions and was moving from place to place to fast to be a conventional aircraft from my point of view. Don't know what it was but it was interesting.
trends: There have been 110 other sightings in Seattle
There were no other sightings in Seattle on or around May 5th 2008
Summary: Pulsating white light high in sky. Everytime light pulsated it was in another part of the sky!
